data.description: Welcome to 401 Hunley Ln, a captivating 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem nestled in the prestigious Arrowhead community of Myrtle Beach. This home exudes charm, elegance, and the perfect blend of modern convenience with a coastal touch. The open and inviting living room, where high ceilings create an airy, spacious atmosphere. The seamless flow of this space effortlessly connects you to the heart of the home, making it ideal for gatherings and relaxation. The kitchen features stylish stainless steel appliances, a generous pantry, a convenient breakfast bar, abundant counter space, and ample cabinet storage. The master bedroom is a sanctuary of comfort and tranquility. Sunlight streams in, enhancing the serene ambiance, while a spacious walk-in closet ensures your wardrobe is beautifully organized. The en-suite master bathroom boasts a dual sink vanity, a roomy walk-in shower, and a luxurious tub where you can unwind and rejuvenate. In addition to the master suite, this home offers three more spacious bedrooms and two additional bathrooms, providing ample space for family, guests, or a home office. A dedicated dining room and an expansive family room bathed in natural light creates the perfect backdrop for memorable gatherings and special occasions. Outside, the front porch invites you to sit back and soak in the sights and sounds of the friendly neighborhood. The back patio is an ideal spot for entertaining or unwinding after a long day. Arrowhead community boasts exceptional amenities, including a sparkling pool and tennis courts, allowing you to stay active and socialize with neighbors just steps from your front door. Location is key, and 401 Hunley Ln delivers. Situated near Highway 501, you'll enjoy easy access to the Arrowhead Country Club and a short drive to the beach, The Intracoastal Waterway, Tanger Outlets on Highway 501, Broadway at the Beach, Coastal Grand Mall, and a multitude of shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Don't miss your opportunity to own this remarkable Myrtle Beach residence. Book your showing today!
